If FILE is not specified, use \fI\,/var/run/utmp\/\fP.  \fI\,/var/log/wtmp\/\fP as FILE is common.
If ARG1 ARG2 given, \fB\-m\fR presumed: 'am i' or 'mom likes' are usual.
